---
interface Props {
  locale?: string;
}
const { locale = 'en' } = Astro.props;

const basePath = locale === 'en' ? '/learn/english' : `/${locale}/learn/english`;
const localized = {
  en: {
    eyebrow: 'Write Better to Speak Better',
    titleTop: 'The Foundation of',
    titleAccent: 'Fluent English',
    intro:
      'A six-step foundation for learners who want to speak confidently. Built on the core structures of English, so the words are there when you need them.',
    method: 'The Method',
    paragraphs: [
      'Real fluency happens in conversation. When you open your mouth, the words are already there. That is what SpeakPath is built for. But to speak without thinking, you need patterns in place first.',
      'Writing is how you build those patterns. When you write a sentence, slow it down, and fix it. You are not learning to write for its own sake. You are loading the structure into memory so it comes out automatically when you speak.',
      'If you are starting from zero, or if grammar has always felt confusing, these lessons are built for you. Work through each section in order. Read the material, write the examples in a notebook to lock the patterns in, and when you feel confident, bring it into SpeakPath and practice speaking until those patterns feel natural in your voice.',
